  "title": "HAIRSTYLIST",
  "description": "<p>SO SALON LOCATED AT THE CATHAY</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>WEBSITE: https://www.sosalon.sg</p>\n<p>IG: https://www.instagram.com/sosalon.sg/?hl=en</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><em><strong>We're Hiring: Hairstylists</strong></em></p>\n<p><em>We are looking for passionate and skilled individuals to join our team. If you are a dedicated hairstylist looking for career growth, a stable customer base, and an opportunity to work in a supportive environment, we would love to hear from you.</em></p>\n<p><em>Location: Central Singapore</em></p>\n<h4><em><strong>Who Can Apply</strong></em></h4>\n<ul>\n  <li><em>Experienced hairstylists are welcome.</em></li>\n</ul>\n<h4><em><strong>Compensation &amp; Benefits</strong></em></h4>\n<ul>\n  <li><em>Hairstylists: Earn up to S$8,000 per month, with competitive commission structures.</em></li>\n  <li><em>Assistants: Starting salary from S$2,000 per month, plus high commission opportunities.</em></li>\n  <li><em>Freelance: Competitive commission structures.</em></li>\n  <li><em>Welcome Bonus for successful candidates.</em></li>\n</ul>\n<h4><em><strong>Why Join Us?</strong></em></h4>\n<ul>\n  <li><em>Stable Customer Base: We provide a consistent flow of clients, so you can focus on your craft without worrying about building a customer base from scratch.</em></li>\n  <li><em>Media Feature Opportunities: Be part of projects that give you exposure in various media platforms, helping to grow your personal and professional brand.</em></li>\n  <li><em>Friendly Working Environment: Work in a positive and collaborative team where mutual support and growth are encouraged.</em></li>\n  <li><em>Training Provided &amp; Career Progression: Whether you are starting out or looking to advance your career, we offer continuous learning opportunities and clear career progression paths.</em></li>\n</ul>\n<h4><em><strong>How to Apply</strong></em></h4>\n<p><em>If you are interested, please WhatsApp +65 8868 8831 with your expected salary and resume.</em></p>\n<p><em>We look forward to having you as part of our team!</em></p>",
